This dashboard project aims to provide a comprehensive analysis of customer reviews for British Airways, focusing on various service metrics collected from March 2016 to October 2023. It visualizes performance indicators such as overall rating, cabin service staff, food and beverages, entertainment, ground service, seat comfort, and value for money. The data is segmented by traveler type, seat type, aircraft, and geographic origin of the reviews, allowing detailed insights into the customer experience across different demographics and aircraft types.
